<li class="ref">
<div id="bib14" class="citation"><span class="label">14.</span> <span class="mixed-citation" data-jats-publication-type="journal"><span class="person-group" data-jats-person-group-type="author"><span class="string-name"><span class="surname">Light</span>, <span class="given-names">J.</span></span> </span><span class="article-title">Toward a definition of communicative competence for individuals using augmentative and alternative communication systems</span>. <span class="source"><em>Augmentative and Alternative Communication</em> </span><em><span class="volume">5</span></em>, <span class="issue">2</span> (<span class="year">1989</span>), <span class="fpage">137</span>–<span class="lpage">144</span>.</span></div>
